[I] C library for encoding, decoding and manipulating JSON data

[T] Jansson is a C library for encoding, decoding and manipulating JSON data.
[T] Its main features and design principles are a simple and intuitive API and
[T] data model, comprehensive documentation, no dependencies on other libraries,
[T] full Unicode support (UTF-8) and an extensive test suite.

[U] https://github.com/akheron/jansson

[A] Petri Lehtinen <petri@digip.org>
[M] Tomas Glozar <tglozar@gmail.com>

[C] extra/development
[F] CROSS NO-LTO.clang

[L] MIT
[V] 2.15.1
[P] X -----5---9 127.190

